data.description: This gorgeous Northwest Aliante Move-In Ready 2974sf home is priced at $350,000! Alarm system, separate family and living rooms. Master Bdrm has a huge retreat (perfect for gym, craft room, baby's room or even potential library, the 3 additional bedrooms include 1 bedroom downstairs are very spacious - all with great closets, upstairs Loft, Stainless steel appliances, garage has epoxy floor. 4/20 new dishwasher & garbage disposal. 10/19 New A/C unit. 6/19: RING security system w/2 solar powered cameras, new flooring throughout, some new triple paned windows,  vinyl wood tile. 9/18 - new 50 gal water heater. Ceiling Fans throughout.  Wonderful Green lawn backyard with covered patio/balcony. NO Neighbors Behind - great for relaxing and spending time under the covered patio or up on the balcony! It's also THIS close to schools, shopping and freeways. All for the amazing price of $350,000!! And again, no rear neighbors with some great mountain & Vegas Strip views from the upstairs balcony.
